headline: Qualcomm Expands Beyond Mobile Chips With Growing AI Edge Story
summary: QUALCOMM is expanding into AI edge computing and on-device AI through new partnerships and venture investments. Recent agreements include work with Lantronix and Safe Pro Group on real-time AI threat detection for drones. The company is also backing SpotDraft, which uses AI to support contract management workflows.
